<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Login</title>
  <!-- CSS only -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('pages/nav'); -%>

  <div class="jumbotron custom-jumbo">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="display-4">MIEA Platform</h1>
      <p class="lead">Medical Image Encryption with Access Control</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      <p>Get started by signing up by clicking on one of the buttons below</p>
      <p class="lead">
      <div class="cta" style="justify-content: center;">
        <form action="/user/signup" class="cta-form" method="GET">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-md" href="/user/signup" role="button">
            User Signup
          </a>
        </form>
        <form action="/doctor/signup" class="cta-form" method="GET">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-md" href="/doctor/signup" role="button">Doctor Signup</a>
        </form>
      </div>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-light">
    <div class="container pt-4 pb-4" id="features">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow">
            <img class="card-img-top"
              data-src="holder.js/100px225?theme=thumb&amp;bg=55595c&amp;fg=eceeef&amp;text=Thumbnail"
              alt="Thumbnail [100%x225]" style="height: 225px; width: 100%; display: block;"
              src="img/encrypt.png"
              data-holder-rendered="true">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Image Encryption</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Medical Image Encryption using Chaotic Map technique. The encrypted image is
                stored in the MongoDB database and is encrypted and decrypted using a Flask API.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow">
            <img class="card-img-top"
              data-src="holder.js/100px225?theme=thumb&amp;bg=55595c&amp;fg=eceeef&amp;text=Thumbnail"
              alt="Thumbnail [100%x225]" style="height: 225px; width: 100%; display: block;"
              src="img/secure-login.png"
              data-holder-rendered="true">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Secure Login</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                MongoDB is also used to store the user details and email is used as the username. The password is stored in the
                database with hashing.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow">
            <img class="card-img-top"
              data-src="holder.js/100px225?theme=thumb&amp;bg=55595c&amp;fg=eceeef&amp;text=Thumbnail"
              alt="Thumbnail [100%x225]" style="height: 225px; width: 100%; display: block;"
              src="img/nodejs-cta.png"
              data-holder-rendered="true">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">NodeJS + Flask API</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                The website is made using NodeJS. NodeJS was selected
                due to its ease of use and Flask was chosed for the API as it is in Python which makes algorithms easy to code.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-custom">
    <div class="container pt-4 pb-4" id="about">
      <h3>About</h3>
      <p>
        
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>


</body>

</html>